 USE
 This sketch takes an image and manipulates the pixels. Nuff said.

 - MouseX & mouseY change the intensity of the pixel filters.
 - Arrow keys UP & DOWN - changes pixel grid resolution.
 - Keys 1,2,3 change the colour mode from/to red, green, blue.
 - key s for exporting hi-res images [ once export is finished, program exits ].

